In the Matter of S.W.
appealed by Phyllis W. No. 101P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Peter Wood, for Phyllis W. Cathy L. Moore, Assistant County Attorney, for Durham County DSS. Wendy Sotolongo, Durham, for Guardian Ad Litem. Prior report: ___ N.C.App. ___, 625 S.E.2d 594 .

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed on the 27th day of February 2006 by Respondent (Phyllis W.) in this matter for discretionary review of the decision of the North Carolina Court of Appeals pursuant to G.S. 7A-31, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
